---
title: Chipotle Shrimp Bowls with Charred Corn-Tomato Salsa
description: Succulent shrimp is topped with sweet and smoky chipotle sauce to add a little flair to your dinner table. Plus, the charred corn and tomato salsa takes things to the next level!
